		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">先驱阵列将滚动而来，接触造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#ffecbf">(仅大世界)</span><span>开局从场地后方门处滚动而来。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/穆什特希尔.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较近时，先驱阵列原地起跳下落，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，先驱阵列向空中抛出8枚水弹，向目标随机洒落，造成<span color="#7fbfff">55%,27.5%,<br/>11%,5.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1087" width="424" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">一段时间后或生命值低于<span color="#ffdfbf">50%</span><span>时，先驱阵列移至场地中央展开「</span><span textDecoration="underline">镇压力场</span><span>」，并向后方放置「</span><span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>」，同时在周围形成单向屏障。机关间歇性朝玩家发射激光，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">35%</span><span>伤害。先驱阵列将持续发射水弹，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>或</span><span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害，每发射一次就移动一小段。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="799" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">先驱阵列使用古月力启动「<span textDecoration="underline">聚流力场</span><span>」，并向空中依次丢出3枚大水泡，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。施放期间持续附着</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，先驱阵列转出炮口，发射一枚普通水弹，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害，随后再发射至多2枚强劲水弹，均造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1087" width="442" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「<span textDecoration="underline">镇压力场</span><span>」持续</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20s</span><span>。超时后，先驱阵列将尝试回收剩余的「</span><span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>」，同时为自身施加</span><span textDecoration="underline">聚水护罩</span><span>，并产生大浪，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">120%</span><span>伤害。回收的机关越多，护罩就越厚。护罩击破后无效果，其将在下次展开力场后移除。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
