		<RichText x="9" y="1173" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">瘫痪</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1224" width="432" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">聚流/镇压力场：半径50m范围内重力减弱，跳起时减速<span color="#ffdfbf">45%</span><span>；同时先驱阵列自身</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+200%</span><span>全抗。<br/>探侦机关：</span><span color="#7fbfff">6水</span><span>盾，离地约3m；冻结后触发</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导/碎冰/融化</span><span>等反应可直接破坏，全部击破后瘫痪先驱阵列</span><span color="#ffdfbf">13s</span><span>。<br/>聚水护罩：</span><span color="#7fbfff">36水</span><span>盾，基础</span><span color="#7fbfff">12水</span><span>，每回收一个机关</span><span color="#7fbfff">+6水</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/穆什特希尔.assets/Image_23.png')" x="596" y="469" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1411" y="799" width="431" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当先驱阵列或「<span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>」陷入冻结状态时，当冻结状态被</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">碎冰</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">融化</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">结晶</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">扩散</span><span>等反应解除时，若为先驱阵列自身则将立即中断「聚流力场」，若为「</span><span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>」则将直接被破坏。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
